title: LEAD TRACKER
description: LEAD TRACKER is a neat chrome extension for tracking sales leads which allows us to save the url of a present tab or add your input which will remain saved until we delete them all.

title: VOICE ASSISTANT
description: This is a project made with complete javascript. This Voice assistant named JARVIS is build in order to recognize your voice and take action according to that. For example: you can  ask where is taj mahal?

title: BlackJack Game
description: This is a project made with  javascript. When you hit start button device will take two cards randomly and you will hit a new card it will check if the sum is 21 or not. If you got 21 as a sum then boom you got a BlackJack!
